data.title: Dean's List
data.meta_description: The Dean's List at Hampden-Sydney College lists those students who have earned at least a 3.3 grade-point average that semester, for at least 15 credit hours of work.
data.text:
The Dean's List at Hampden-Sydney College is compiled at the end of each semester. It lists those students who have earned at least a 3.3 grade-point average that semester, for at least 15 credit hours of work.

Spring 2024
